===一門花色===
只剩棍棒、或硬幣的一門花色。除入の吉、金青山保留一到十二的序數牌外<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.asahi-net.or.jp/~rp9h-tkhs/dg_irino.htm|title=地方札・入の吉|language=ja|publisher=HOME PAGE of HIRONORI TAKAHASHI|author=高橋浩德|date=|accessdate=2014-12-11|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304211215/http://www.asahi-net.or.jp/~rp9h-tkhs/dg_irino.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.asahi-net.or.jp/~rp9h-tkhs/dg_kinse.htm|title=地方札・金青山|language=ja|publisher=HOME PAGE of HIRONORI TAKAHASHI|author=高橋浩德|date=|accessdate=2014-12-11|archive-date=2015-09-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150923221523/http://www.asahi-net.or.jp/~rp9h-tkhs/dg_kinse.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>，其他變體的序數牌只剩一到十，張數多剩四十張，有些增一到兩張鬼牌、或空白牌。

